data.title: Urban Future
data.meta_description: Urban Future brings together more than 100 organisations, NGOs and businesses partners to drive change for urban sustainability.
data.text:
Urban Future is an event that is driven by a powerful community with a mission:

it brings together more than 100 organisations, NGOs, businesses, and supporting partners in the effort to connect the world’s most passionate change-makers – with the ultimate goal of speeding up the transformation of cities.

THANK YOU TO ALL OUR PARTNERS from near and far!

We couldn’t do this without you. 🩷

Urban Future looks forward to teaming up with the most exciting networks, organisations and companies that strive to change our cities for the better. Wether you are interested in a networking or business partnership or would like to showcase at our exhibition area – we’d love to talk through your options.

Intrigued? We can’t wait to hear from you!
